  "text": "Would the half moon on the crown represent the receptivity of the subconscious mind. I M Ra. This symbol is not given by Ara, but it is not distasteful for within your own culture. The moon represents the feminine, the sun, the masculine. Thusly, we accept this portion as a portion of the image. For it seems without significant distortion.",
